'''2017年美军裸照丑闻'''是指在[[社交媒体|社交媒体]]上有人发布[[美军|美军]]现役[[女兵|女兵]][[裸照|裸照]]的丑闻，涉及数百名女兵以及美军各大[[军种|军种]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-39227547|title=US military nude photo sharing scandal widens beyond Marines|accessdate=2017-03-10|date=2017-03-10|website=BBC|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015928/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-39227547|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[美國海軍犯罪調查局|美國海軍犯罪調查局]]已启动调查。

== 经过 ==
2017年3月，美国媒体报道了这一事件<ref name="revealnews">{{cite web|url=https://www.revealnews.org/blog/hundreds-of-marines-investigated-for-sharing-photos-of-naked-colleagues/|title=Hundreds of Marines investigated for sharing photos of naked colleagues|accessdate=2017-03-10|date=2017-03-04|last1=Brennan|first1=Thomas James|website=Revealnews.org|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114143509/https://www.revealnews.org/blog/hundreds-of-marines-investigated-for-sharing-photos-of-naked-colleagues/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在一个名为“Marines United”的封闭[[Facebook|Facebook]]小组中，有3万名美军现役、退役军人和[[英国皇家海军陆战队|英国皇家海军陆战队]]退役军人。此小组发布了数百名来自各个军种的女性现役军人的照片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/nude-photo-marine-corps-pentagon-scandal-2017-3|title=The Marine Corps' nude-photo-sharing scandal is even worse than first realized|accessdate=2017-03-10|date=2017-03-09|last1=Szoldra|first1=Paul|website=Business Insider|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805193731/https://www.businessinsider.com/nude-photo-marine-corps-pentagon-scandal-2017-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>，页面包含的[[Dropbox|Dropbox]]和[[Google_Drive|Google云端硬盘]]链接中还有更多照片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2017/03/06/518767235/sharing-of-nude-photos-of-female-marines-prompts-pentagon-investigation|title=Sharing Of Nude Photos Of Female Marines Online Prompts Pentagon Investigation|accessdate=2017-03-06|date=2017-03-06|last1=Chappell|first1=Bill|website=NPR|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715044738/https://www.npr.org/sections/thetwo-way/2017/03/06/518767235/sharing-of-nude-photos-of-female-marines-prompts-pentagon-investigation|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NBC NCIS">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/nude-photo-posts-female-marines-being-investigated-ncis-n729541|title=Nude Photo Posts of Female Marines Being Investigated by NCIS|accessdate=2017-03-10|date=2017-03-06|publisher=Associated Press|website=NBC News|location=Washington|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020422/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/nude-photo-posts-female-marines-being-investigated-ncis-n729541|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一个名为“Marines United 2”的小组有3000名成员。<ref>{{cite web|last1=McLaughlin|first1=Eliott C.|last2=Stapleton|first2=AnneClaire|title=Secret Marines group is still sharing nude photos amid scandal|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/03/08/politics/marines-united-photos-investigation/|website=CNN|accessdate=2017-03-10|date=2017-03-09|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031051221/https://www.cnn.com/2017/03/08/politics/marines-united-photos-investigation/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Daily Beast">{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2017/03/10/marines-keep-sharing-women-s-nude-photos-in-secret-groups-after-getting-busted.html|title=Marines Keep Sharing Women’s Nude Photos in Secret Groups After Getting Busted|accessdate=2017-03-10|date=2017-03-10|last1=LaPorta|first1=James|last2=Laverty|first2=Rory|website=The Daily Beast|archive-date=2017-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170531053519/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2017/03/10/marines-keep-sharing-women-s-nude-photos-in-secret-groups-after-getting-busted.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

据《[[商业内幕|商业内幕]]》报道，除Facebook外，女兵的裸照还被上传到一个名叫“AnonIB”的影像分享留言板，在这个专门为军方人员设立的留言板上，有十几个帖子都要求特定女兵的裸照，而且还提供相关女兵的姓名以及驻扎地点<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://mil.huanqiu.com/world/2017-03/10291796.html|title=美国女兵裸照丑闻扩及各军种 丑闻惊动美军高层|accessdate=2017-03-19|author=陈欣|date=2017-03-11|publisher=环球网|archive-date=2017-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170613073342/http://mil.huanqiu.com/world/2017-03/10291796.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反應==
=== 美國軍方 ===
事件曝光後，[[美國海軍犯罪調查局|美國海軍犯罪調查局]]已對此启动调查<ref name="NBC NCIS"/>。[[美国国防部长|美国国防部长]][[詹姆斯·马蒂斯|詹姆斯·马蒂斯]]称“民间和军事人员在社交媒体网站上的所谓行动，包括一些与海军陆战队以及其他可能军种有关的行动，极度背离军方的基本价值观。”<ref name="Daily Beast"/> [[美国海军陆战队司令|美国海军陆战队司令]][[罗伯特·内勒|罗伯特·内勒]]表示“在网上或其他地方攻击我们海军陆战队的人，令人厌恶，是对隊员的不尊重”。海军陆战队總士官長罗纳德·L·格林（Ronald L. Green）说“这种负面行为与我们所代表的形象完全相反。”海军陆战队发言人瑞恩·埃尔维斯（Ryan Alvis）感谢托马斯·布雷南（Thomas Brennan）揭发这一丑闻，表示“这让我们能立刻采取行动，删除照片，并且做好帮助那些受害者的准备。”<ref name="NBC NCIS"/>

=== 美国国会 ===
[[美国参议院军事委员会|美国参议院军事委员会]]成员[[基爾斯滕·吉利布蘭德|基爾斯滕·吉利布蘭德]]呼吁就事件进行[[听证会|听证会]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Helsel|first1=Phil|title=Senator Calls for Hearing Over Marines Nude Photo Scandal|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/senator-calls-hearing-over-marines-nude-photo-scandal-n730911|website=NBC News|accessdate=2017-03-10|date=2017-03-08|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125030627/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/senator-calls-hearing-over-marines-nude-photo-scandal-n730911|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美国众议院军事委员会|美国众议院军事委员会]]副主席[[亞當·史密斯_(政治家)|亞當·史密斯]]称网上的行为“有辱人格，十分危险，完全不可接受。”<ref name="NBC NCIS"/>

